HEADWORD: Saintlike
<hw>Saint"like`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Resembling a
saint; suiting a saint; becoming a saint; saintly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Glossed over only with a <qex>saintlike</qex> show.</q>
